      <title>美国大选焦虑或为韩国债券创造购买机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/us-election-angst-may-create-buying-opportunity-for-korean-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者和分析师表示，今年晚些时候美国大选引发的波动性加剧可能为购买韩国债券提供良好机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/us-election-angst-may-create-buying-opportunity-for-korean-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
