    <item>
      <title>美联航预计降低机票价格，利润下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-17/united-expects-lower-profits-as-it-cuts-ticket-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联合航空表示，由于降价以跟上廉价航空公司的步伐，其第三季度利润将低于分析师预期。这些举措正在影响整个行业。彭博情报的乔治·弗格森在“彭博收盘”节目中讨论了这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-17/united-expects-lower-profits-as-it-cuts-ticket-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织敦促二十国集团制定计划降低穷国债务成本并避免违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/imf-to-push-g-20-for-plan-to-lower-debt-costs-for-poor-countries-avoid-defaults</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织正在寻求团结二十国集团采取新的举措，帮助贫穷国家减轻债务负担、避免违约并稳定其经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/imf-to-push-g-20-for-plan-to-lower-debt-costs-for-poor-countries-avoid-defaults</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
